安装python的包管理工具andpython的arff包

---------------------------------------------------------------
安装python的包管理工具
sudo apt-get install python-pip
---------------------------------
安装后
whereos pip
pip: /usr/bin/pip /usr/bin/X11/pip /usr/share/man/man1/pip.1.gz
which pip
/usr/bin/pip
------------------------------------------------------------------

安装python的包
arff0.9
sudo pip install arff
------------------
安装后
pip show arff 
---
Name: arff
Version: 0.9
Location: /usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages
Requires: 
